trans-unit.source: Specifies Cryptography Next Generation (CNG) key property options.
trans-unit.target: Angir kryptografi neste generasjon (CNG) nøkkelegenskapen alternativer.

trans-unit.source: These options are used to initialize <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CngProperty> objects, which are then used in <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CngKey.SetProperty%2A> calls.
trans-unit.target: Disse alternativene brukes til å initialisere <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CngProperty>objekter, som deretter brukes i <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CngKey.SetProperty%2A>kall.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CngKey.SetProperty%2A> </xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CngProperty>

trans-unit.source: You also use these options when you query for the value of properties with the <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CngKey.GetProperty%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Du også bruke disse alternativene når du vil søke etter verdien til egenskaper med den <xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CngKey.GetProperty%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Security.Cryptography.CngKey.GetProperty%2A>

trans-unit.source: Properties must be queried with the CngPropertyOptions they are stored with.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapene må spørres med CngPropertyOptions de er lagret med.

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, they will not be found.
The property is not specified by CNG.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen er ikke angitt av CNG.

trans-unit.source: Use this option to avoid future name conflicts with CNG properties.
trans-unit.target: Bruk dette alternativet for å unngå fremtidige er i konflikt med CNG-egenskaper.

trans-unit.source: The referenced property has no options.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen refereres til, har ingen alternativer.
